Requirements
-----------------------------------------------
SilverStripe 3.0

Documentation
-----------------------------------------------
Not yet ready

Installation Instructions
-----------------------------------------------
1) see http://doc.silverstripe.org/modules:simple_guestbook for further information and instructions
2) Copy the modules:guestbook directory into your main SilverStripe directory
-- 3) add the required modules reCaptcha and spamprotection
4) run /dev/Build/
5) run ?flush=all

Usage Overview
-----------------------------------------------

Known issues:
-----------------------------------------------
Entry commenting don't works
Spam protection don't works
Smilies don't works
Don't used SpamProtectionModule
Don't used ReCaptchaModule
Don't used PHPCaptcha module